How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
4 out of 5 stars
Great Watch - No Silence for Games
This is a great youth's watch. It does so much stuff. It will occupy your child for a long time. It has a stopwatch, games, takes pictures, tracks steps and can even give them reminders when they should be brushing their teeth. Great value for the money.. There are a bunch of options to pick for the watch face design.My only grip is the volume button doesn't seem to control the games. A great time to use the games on the watch would be when they need to be quiet, but occupied. The noise the games make prevents them from using it in certain situations.If it wasn't for the game sound it would be perfect.*It should be noted that the camera quality is pretty terrible, but I don't think anybody is taking professional photoshoots with a child's watch.
